      "This isn’t vaporware or another stablecoin chained to a dying dollar. TEXITcoin is a real currency: proof-of-work secured, fixed supply (353 million coins over 138 years), fast peer-to-peer transactions with low fees, and a decentralized mine built right here in the Lone Star State. Mining isn’t just a gimmick—it’s energy, effort, and value creation. That’s how real money has always worked, and that’s how TEXITcoin works.",
      "Crypto is full of lies, but TEXITcoin confronts risk head-on. We’ve faced regulatory hurdles (the February 2026 cease-and-desist order from the Texas State Securities Board), bank account closures, and the usual noise from those who fear what we represent. We don’t hide from it—we address it openly, cooperate where required, and keep building. Scams promise guaranteed riches with no effort; we promise a real shot at something bigger—if you show up, contribute, and believe. Visionaries acknowledge the risk and build anyway.",
